  {panel}

Implement the ability to automatically link issues.

Turn it on / off from the Issue Linking screen. When turning it on, you may want to build links between all existing issues.

How it would work is every time a comment or worklog is created, if there are issue keys mentioned - a link is created between the two issues. Maybe hardcoded "References" issue link type?
